These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, action, mystery, time-travel, family, adventure, sports
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: dubstep, ambient, d&b, salsa, trance, disco, indie
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, lacrosse, biathlon, skateboarding, weightlifting, snowboarding, cycling
 1. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is between the fan of ambient and the fan of dubstep##2
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the fan of salsa is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person watching family movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
10. the person watching sports movies is the fan of d&b##1
11. the fan of disco is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
13. the person who's sport is soccer is the fan of trance##1
14. the person watching adventure movies is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | crime     | adventure | action | time-travel | sports  | mystery  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | salsa        | ambient  | indie     | disco   | d&b       | trance   |
| Sport         | lacrosse   | cycling | skateboarding    | biathlon  | weightlifting | snowboarding | soccer |

