.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: mexican, turkish, italian, spanish, russian, brazilian, dutch
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, surfing, climbing, ice-hockey, rowing, golf, skateboarding
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile, skateboard, jet-ski, helicopter, subway, quad-bike
 1. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is the dutch##1
 6. the mexican is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the mexican is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the russian##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
10. the italian is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the russian is on the right of the mexican##1
12. the person driving the airplane is the turkish##1
13. the spanish is on the left of the mexican##1
14. the spanish is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
15. the turkish is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | dutch      | spanish     | mexican  | russian | italian | turkish |
