10. the firefighter is on the right of the fisherman##1
11. the person driving the boat is the bartender##1
12. the firefighter is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the writer##1
14. the person driving the tram is the person drinking juice##1
