.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  videographer, dressmaker, mechanic, paramedic, scientist, social-worker, pilot
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, electronic, ambient, blues, dubstep, jazz
7 different pets are kept: dog, pony, rabbit, rat, goat, turtle, frog
 1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the mechanic##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is between the fan of blues and the fan of electronic##2
 3. the fan of hip-hop is the owner of the pony##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the left of the social-worker##1
 5. the fan of hip-hop is the videographer##1
 6. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 7. the scientist is the fan of dubstep##1
 8. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is the owner of the pony##1
10. the pilot is the owner of the goat##1
11. the videographer is on the right of the paramedic##1
12. the fan of jazz is on the left of the social-worker##1
13. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
14. the fan of indie is on the left of the videographer##1
15. the pilot is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | dressmaker | social-worker | scientist | mechanic  | pilot   | paramedic | videographer      |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | electronic        | dubstep    | blues     | ambient     | indie   | hip-hop        |
| Pet           | dog   | rabbit       | turtle    | rat | goat | frog   | pony |

