.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, writing, board-games, collecting, chess, reading, card-games
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, ferret, bird, rabbit, chinchilla, pony, mouse
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, tram, train, jet-ski, roller, bike, helicopter
 1. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 2. the person driving the helicopter is the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the roller##1
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the owner of the chinchilla##1
13. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the pony##1
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the van##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Hobby       | board-games  | reading | collecting  | card-games | writing | chess | skydiving |
| Pet         | rabbit | bird    | guinea-pig        | chinchilla      | pony     | ferret   | mouse |
| Transport   | train  | tram   | roller | bike        | jet-ski    | helicopter  | van   |

