.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-18::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: epic, zombie, fantasy, superhero, documentary, mystery, time-travel
7 different pets are kept: frog, rabbit, chinchilla, snake, ferret, dog, cat
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, badminton, tennis, handball, rugby, ice-hockey
 1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person who's sport is handball##2
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
11. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the snake##1
12. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
13. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
15. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |     7      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | zombie    | documentary  | mystery        | epic | fantasy | superhero     |
| Pet           | rabbit | snake | cat     | dog      | ferret     | frog     | chinchilla    |
| Sport         | sailing   | rugby  | badminton | snowboarding | handball    | tennis  | ice-hockey |

