.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-19::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  software-developer, paramedic, fisherman, librarian, manager, entrepreneur, social-worker
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: fantasy, spy, family, romance, mystery, horror, animation
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: climbing, basketball, weightlifting, cricket, sailing, water-polo, tennis
 1. the librarian is on the left of the social-worker##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 5. the entrepreneur is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the social-worker is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 9. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the paramedic##1
12. the person who's sport is climbing is between the fisherman and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
13. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
14. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
15. the software-developer is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |      4      |      5       |      6      |      7       |
| Job           | fisherman      | software-developer | manager | paramedic   | entrepreneur | librarian | social-worker |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | family   | fantasy   | romance | spy        | mystery       | horror       |
| Sport         | basketball    | climbing       | water-polo   | cricket      | tennis   | weightlifting  | sailing |

