.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, soy-milk, lemonade, juice, water, hot-chocolate
The people have 7 different hobbies: cooking, fishing, camping, woodworking, chess, drawing, card-games
7 different pets are kept: goat, fish, chinchilla, turtle, hedgehog, bird, rabbit
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the bird is the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's hobby is camping and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
13. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
15. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | water   | juice   | lemonade        | soy-milk     | milk | mirinda       |
| Hobby      | cooking | fishing | card-games | woodworking | camping  | chess   | drawing |
| Pet        | rabbit   | fish     | goat     | bird      | hedgehog | turtle    | chinchilla      |

 